('Perplexity AI', 'AI-powered search engine that answers questions with cited sources. Real-time internet access with GPT-4 quality responses.', 'Search', 'https://perplexity.ai', 'Free/Pro', 4.7, '{"Research","Search","Q&A","Citations"}', '{"Search","Research","Citations","Real-time"}', true, false, 9200),
