('Sora', 'OpenAI''s text-to-video model. Create realistic videos up to 60 seconds from text descriptions. Revolutionary video generation.', 'Video Generation', 'https://openai.com/sora', 'Waitlist', 4.6, '{"Video creation","Marketing","Content","Film"}', '{"Video","Text-to-Video","OpenAI","Generation"}', false, false, 7600),
