('Notion AI', 'AI writing, summarizing, and organizing built into Notion. Write faster, summarize documents, and manage knowledge effortlessly.', 'Productivity', 'https://notion.so', 'Free/Add-on', 4.4, '{"Writing","Summaries","Notes","Project management"}', '{"Productivity","Notes","Writing","Organization"}', false, false, 8900),
